org.apache.ctakes.core.concurrent

Interface ThreadSafeWrapper<AE extends org.apache.uima.fit.component.JCasAnnotator_ImplBase>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.apache.uima.analysis_component.AnalysisComponent

    public interface ThreadSafeWrapper<AE extends org.apache.uima.fit.component.JCasAnnotator_ImplBase>
extends org.apache.uima.analysis_component.AnalysisComponent
    To take advantage of singletons for thread safety and enums for singletons, utilize jdk 8+ interface default methods so that enums can implement AnalysisComponent without boilerplate code for every method.
    Since:
    11/20/2017
    Version:
    %I%
    Author:
    SPF , chip-nlp
